ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder No. 169 - (British Columbia) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 169 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of BRITISH COLUMBIA with respect to the FLOODING causing damage to private property, small businesses, First Nation communities and infrastructure in the eastern, south central and south western parts of the province from June 18, 2012 to July 8, 2012.
